x-sizing: border-box;\">다음과 같이 안내하오니 관심 있는 학생들은 해당 기간 내에 신청하시기 바랍니다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1. </span>대상<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>지원자격<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) : 2026-1</span>학기 재학생<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(6</span>학점 이내<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">), </span>휴학생<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(3</span>학점 이내<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\">              <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">※ </span>단, 8월 졸업 예정 학생 제외</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2. </span>신청기간 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">~ 2026. 05. 06.(수) 17:00 </span>까지</span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">            </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">※ 첨부된 파일 내 명시된 접수기간은 '대학' 접수 기한으로, 학생은 반드시 <u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">05월 06일</u>까지 신청</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3. 신청방법 : </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">상단 첨부파일을 참조하여 </span></span></span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">nDRIMS</span></span></u></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 신청 후</u> 해당 신청 기한 까지 <u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">본교 학사지원팀(본관 3층, 남산홀 맞은편)</u>에 신청원 제출</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">            <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">※ <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">전공으로 인정 원할시 반드시 <u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">제출 전 해당과목 주임교수 확인 必</u></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">           </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(204, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\">※